==Mandarin==

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī yĭn yī zhúo, mò fēi qían dìng

===Phrase===
'''[[一]][[饮]][[一]][[啄]]，[[莫]][[非]][[前]][[定]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') From every single drink to every single bite, there is nothing that is not preordained.

===Alternate forms===
[[一]][[飲]][[一]][[啄]]，[[莫]][[非]][[前]][[定]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

